    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Choral angels are singers of great skill, and their ranks fill the halls of good deities with soaring hymns and solemn chants. They manifest from the spirits of the pious dead who had exceptional musical talent. While they aren\u2019t soldiers, chorals can defend themselves with their magical voices. Chorals sometimes visit the Material Plane with auspicious messages for mortals."
        }
    ],
